Beardbrand
September 6 at 9:01 PM ·

Watch Eric's beard go from naturally full, to full of awesomeness. Here's how Eric's morning ritual help him achieve this style:

Step 1) Wash Beard & Apply Beard Softener
Step 2) Damp dry beard
Step 3) Mix together 1/2 amount Utility Balm + 1/2 amount of Beard Oil and apply to beard and skin...
Step 4) Blow dry beard, from left to right, then from right to left, then from neck to chin.
Step 5) Blow dry mustache from middle to tips. Comb to shape
Step 6) Fluff beard with fingers, and comb with large brush to final shape

Show us your before and after photo. Tag @beardbrand in your transformation.
